summary: Adds trap doors and moves one Stone of Barenziah
descriptionHtml:
Adds trap doors and moves one Stone of Barenziah, letting you collect all 24 without having to use the console or enter factions.

-Adds trap door near bottom of the Mage\'s Guild
-Adds trap door to DB Sanctuary
-Adds an additional stone to the Blue Palace.

Bugs:
Talking to NPCs may cause some quest bugs. Backup your saves if you intend to do these quests later.
author: Slayermaster
